Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.25,sign_2572_1_Sender__Morioka_,# phone,0000,0000,0000,,Sender: Morioka Moriko \NRecipient: Sakurai Yuta \N\NSubject: Thank you for your consideration \N\NDear Sakurai Yuta,\N I apologize for sending this reply so late. \NI was touched by your response to my original email.\NThank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.42,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Sh-She sent a reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.89,EP Number,# title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.89,EP Title,# title,0000,0000,0000,,You and I, the Cowards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.53,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Koiwai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.40,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,That piece isn't cooked, so don't take it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:17.65,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? You're so picky. \NAre you blood type A?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.18,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.32,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I'm type O.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.28,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,So I go with the flow, whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.61,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,What does that even matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.04,sign_3533_12_Blood_types_have,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,1)}*Blood types actually have nothing to do with personality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.42,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get back to the question at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.29,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Sakura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.23,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Also, why do you call me "Sakura-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.68,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Man, type A people are real sticklers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:44.05,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Let's just \Nenjoy this all-you-can-eat meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.81,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,You used to work at Matsukaze Bussan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:55.10,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,You know your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.18,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from our \Nsoon-to-be department head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.82,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,full speed ahead on the elite path,\N Sakurai Yuta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:04.95,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Morioka Moriko-san? She worked in the distribution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.83,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,systems department at Matsukaze Bussan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:09.51,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Morioka Moriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.21,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Morimori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.13,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Morimori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.97,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with Morimori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.45,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by this manual she wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:22.54,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed she was extremely competent\Nand must be good at her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.25,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently she resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.16,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Morimori-chan was definitely good at her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:33.98,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Um, would you mind telling me why \Nyou keep calling her Morimori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.56,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,It's the nickname I gave her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:36.73,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,How close were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:41.33,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,That said, it's not like \Nwe were friends or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:44.55,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,But when I called her \Ndepartment at the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.85,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,she filled in for the person\N in charge sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.88,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for taking the call. \NMy name is Morioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.65,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima isn't available at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.79,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,so if you don't mind,\N I'd be happy to help instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.32,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.89,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you look over \Nsome documents for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:01.18,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please send them over. \NI'll tell you when I get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.66,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Koiwai-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:09.06,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it will probably take me\N thirty minutes or so to go through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.52,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.90,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.27,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Morioka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.17,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for bothering you \Nwhen you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.65,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,You sound really beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:24.03,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. I was trying my best to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.55,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel. Don't let it get \Nto you. Thanks for working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.58,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.75,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's wrong? \NYou're so tired you're crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.61,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.99,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.80,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,If you're all alone there, \Nthen go ahead and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.62,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all alone here, too, Mori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.57,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.28,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't like being called Mori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.30,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's your given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:52.22,Flashback_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,M-Moriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.15,sign_7008_63_Morioka_Moriko,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,150)}Morioka {\c&H22F01A&}Moriko
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.06,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Mori and Mori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.06,sign_7008_63_Morioka_Moriko,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,1)}Mori    {\c&H22F01A&}Mori
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.80,Flashback,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,So Morimori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.19,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.80,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.34,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Here! This is a picture of Morimori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.00,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.95,sign_7354_71_Matsukaze__Bussa,# tablet,0000,0000,0000,,Matsukaze \NBussan\N Systems
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.27,Main_Italics,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,So it really is her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.76,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,She was pretty good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.44,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what she's up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.90,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should meet up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:32.53,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.53,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you dropped your \Nchopsticks, Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.86,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember raising you \Nto be such a vulgar child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.61,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, one fell on the floor. \NCan you pick it up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:49.03,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's way more \Non your side than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.62,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd the other one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.54,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,It was on the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.75,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.29,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a new set.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.63,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.05,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you \Ndidn't hold them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.95,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,So this is my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.32,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you talk \Nto your elders that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.34,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan, Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:22.04,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Which chopsticks did you drop? \NThese clean ones? Or these dirty ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.40,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Koiwai, they both fell on the floor,\Nso they're both dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.41,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Our break's almost over, so please \Njust hand me some new chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.67,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,Relax a little, Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.61,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go pick up some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.05,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you back at the office then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:08.07,sign_2572_1_Sender__Morioka_,# phone,0000,0000,0000,,The bruise on my forehead disappeared completely after a couple days.\N Thank you for your concern.\N As for your suggestion to go out to celebrate my recovery,\N when I consider that it was my fault for not watching where I was going\N and that you already paid for my medical treatment,\N I'm afraid I couldn't possibly trouble you any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:07.68,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,As for your suggestion to go \Nout to celebrate my recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.77,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,when I consider that it was my fault\N for not watching where I was going,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.21,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,and that you already paid \Nfor my medical treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.31,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I couldn't possibly \Ntrouble you any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.98,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a lot's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:41.10,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd get an email from a man
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.47,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,asking to take me out to dinner to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.12,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:16.35,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought really hard about how \Nto word my reply to Sakurai-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:20.81,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best to be polite and sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.31,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Right. In my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.95,Main,Fujimoto,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she's in a good \Nmood for some reason today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.69,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,And now I feel completely refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.73,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:53.03,Main,Fujimoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.78,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.10,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:33.10,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:41.38,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can log in with nothing \Nweighing on my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.18,sign_13899_116_Log_in,# computer,0000,0000,0000,,Log in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:51.56,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more refreshing\N than an online game!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.21,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Pokotarou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.15,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.96,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hayashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.47,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,By the look of it, it seems you\N got through what was troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.88,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it from Li-chan. \NShe said you were worried about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.22,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,So the secret's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.68,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't think too badly of her for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.98,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's just worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.38,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,They're afraid you'll stop logging in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.32,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,because you're so preoccupied \Nwith things in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.59,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.51,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,But I think my relationship with \Ngames works the other way around,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.24,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe it just doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.30,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:47.75,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,When I've got something on my mind, \NI feel like gaming is my salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.62,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Right? I get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.01,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,But now that everything's been resolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.00,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm refreshed and ready to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.80,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,So everything's all worked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.30,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, thanks! Everything's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.06,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.19,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you got a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.70,sign_16225_140_New_message_,# computer,0000,0000,0000,,New message
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.70,sign_16225_141_You_ve_received_,# computer,0000,0000,0000,,You've received a present from {\c&Hbf4de8&}Lily-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.70,sign_16225_142_Accept,# computer,0000,0000,0000,,Accept
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.70,sign_16225_143_Close,# computer,0000,0000,0000,,Close
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:21.41,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I've received a present from Lily-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.45,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! From Lily-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:31.96,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,This looks expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.96,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.96,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, I have to give \Nher something as thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.47,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I owe her big now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:47.51,sign_16867_153_Crafting_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Crafting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:49.48,sign_16867_151_Spell_Scrolls_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Spell Scrolls
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:49.48,sign_16867_152_in_inventory,# text,0000,0000,0000,,in inventory
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:48.57,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can see how that'd \Nmake you feel as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.48,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:56.57,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Normally it should be the guy \Nwho's on the ball with this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:01.85,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I come bearing a brilliant \Nten billion karat gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.10,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.17,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to have it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.20,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,as a sign of my devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.29,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's how a man should\N treat a lady. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.87,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with your image of masculinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:18.63,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's starting to influence me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.13,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.09,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wanted to thank her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.09,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san can already buy something \Nthat costs this many points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.18,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,She must have quite a bit of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.68,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,If I tried to give her something in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:36.16,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,she'd probably already have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.64,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sort of thing can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.44,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I know the feeling. That happened \Nto me when I first started too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.45,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You know our guildmate Nico?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:57.13,sign_18401_172_I_only_give_to_p,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3750,1)}I only give to people I want to cheer on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.34,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Nico-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:53.04,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know her, but we've\N done a couple of quests together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.13,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She gave me an amazing \Nweapon out of nowhere once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.75,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how you'd be \Na bit taken aback by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.13,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Right? I don't like feeling indebted \Nto other people, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.10,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually pretty upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:07.64,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:12.64,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,She told me it was just a prior \Ninvestment, and I ended up taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.64,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,A prior investment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.12,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.19,Flashback,Nico,0000,0000,0000,,No one loses here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:22.04,Flashback,Nico,0000,0000,0000,,You can just thank me \Nwith your attitude, Pokotarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.38,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,So, well, I guess that's where it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.95,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,She'd always help me out, and I'd always \Ntry to thank her in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.95,sign_19317_187_Spell_Scroll_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1050,1)}Spell Scroll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.95,sign_19334_188_in_inventory,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1050,1)}in inventory
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.95,sign_19343_189_Crafting_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1050,1)}Crafting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.83,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason that's continued
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:34.58,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,is because, when all's said and done,\N Nico just wants to cheer me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.04,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Lily-chan's the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.84,sign_19636_194_Crafting,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Crafting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.84,sign_19636_194_Spell_Scroll_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Spell Scroll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.84,sign_19636_195_in_inventory,# text,0000,0000,0000,,in inventory
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.84,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,There, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.84,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,So what are these things you've been making?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:47.09,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're spell scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.78,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,You normally need a staff to cast spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:53.35,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,but if you put the magic \Ninto a scroll, anyone can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.77,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Hayashi-kun, I'd suggest not \Nthinking too hard about that gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.28,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably fine just to keep whatever \Nulterior motives Lily-chan might have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.23,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.36,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.49,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,U-Ulterior motives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.37,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,What ulterior motives could she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.86,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san's ulterior motives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.69,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. I keep thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.03,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.23,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:56.08,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I was just thinking through some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:13.35,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thanks a lot for giving me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:17.73,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I guess maybe it \Ndidn't suit your tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.23,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.19,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,How should I broach the subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:33.78,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if you had some kind \Nof ulterior motive in giving me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.16,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,U-Ulterior motive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.29,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I just came right out and said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:43.86,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I mean, I was just thinking \Nthat I'd feel bad if you did because
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.67,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing I can give you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.30,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,B-But ulterior motives? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:52.30,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, I just thought maybe... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.05,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like that, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.35,Main_Italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,He looks disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:01.06,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I have absolutely none.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.66,Main_Italics,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,So you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:09.13,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Hayashi-san, can I tell \Nyou a bit about myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.44,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.99,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear it. I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:17.99,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I first started playing this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:18.99,sign_23458_232_Lily_san_has_log,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san has logged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:23.25,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I used to get quite a few requests \Nto go hunting with people every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.50,sign_23484_233_Oh__it_s_Lily_sa,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Lily-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.00,sign_23501_234_It_s_Lily_san__,# text,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lily-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.37,sign_23525_235_Good_evening__,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.00,sign_23539_237_Shi_san_has_invi,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Shi-san{\c&H1e1c1f&\b0} has invited you to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.08,sign_23545_238_Rinarina_san_has,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Rinarina-san{\b0} {\c&H1e1c1f&}has invited you to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.08,sign_23551_239_Torippi_san_has_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Torippi-san{\b0} {\c&H1e1c1f&}has invited you to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:22.87,sign_23557_240_riden_san_has_in,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}riden-san{\b0} {\c&H1e1c1f&}has invited you to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.29,Chat base,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:26.04,Chat base,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Join my party!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.79,Chat base,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, hey!\NMy waifu!\NYou're so cute, Lily-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.25,Chat base,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, hey!\NLily-san!!\NLily-chan!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.32,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Up until then, all my parties had been PUGs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.89,sign_23844_245_Hey__Lily_san_,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lily-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.80,Main_Top,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lily-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:40.14,sign_23865_243_A_pick_up_group_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,350)}A pick-up group, or PUG, is a party formed when a group of strangers\N get together because they have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:36.96,Main_Top,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:40.44,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,so part of it was because I was just always \Ngrouping up with random people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.64,sign_23890_247_Hello___,# pink,0000,0000,0000,,Hello ^^
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:39.10,sign_23900_250_That_last_group_,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,That last group was fun. \NLet's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.21,Main_Top,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That last group was fun. Let's do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.54,Main_Top,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.81,sign_23965_252_Thanks____,# pink,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks~ ^^
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:45.02,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,But once I entered a guild, \NI got to know quite a few people,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:45.40,sign_24019_254_Lily_san__,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}Lily-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:48.27,sign_24025_255_Lily_san_,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}Lily-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.52,sign_24037_256_Lily_san_,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}Lily-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.77,sign_24043_257_Hello_,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:48.27,sign_24055_258_Why_didn_t_you_s,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:48.27,sign_24079_261_There_she_is__,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.35,sign_24088_260_It_s_been_a_whil,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.27,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,and I started getting even more whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.61,sign_24105_264_Hello__,# pink,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.27,sign_24105_263_What_are_you_doi,# blue,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:52.78,sign_24175_266_Popularity_of_a_,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Popularity of a support role
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.46,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:58.46,Flashback,woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with our leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.04,Flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Wh-What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.04,Flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any closer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.03,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you went through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.55,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a misunderstanding, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.67,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're all online,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:24.03,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,it's still pretty difficult to \Nhandle social relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:24.56,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:27.94,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I kept having that kind of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.94,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been easy to just quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:35.28,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,but I really wanted to keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:38.49,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:44.08,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I met someone really precious \Nto me in a game I used to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:49.41,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get to see them anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.85,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,but I kept thinking \Nhow wonderful it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.65,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,if I could meet someone else like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.09,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.47,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.97,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:05.23,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,I used to play a game with someone \Nwho always gave me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:14.67,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,So I completely understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:18.61,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Right. And that's why, even when it was hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.45,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep playing this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:26.29,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,And then Kanbe-san came along \Nand gave me some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:31.27,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, given how you look, \Nit's no surprise you're so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.92,Flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,But I just want to have fun and play\N the game like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.41,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you try being so over \Nthe top that everyone doubts your gender?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:42.43,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,"I love pink, frills, flowers, \Nstrawberries, forests,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.27,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,and little squirrels frolicking!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.06,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:50.19,Flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever act that obnoxious, \NI'm sure I'd lose {\i1}all{\i0} of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.31,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,No dice? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.69,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Just say you're my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.38,Flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.20,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:04.20,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,But if you say you're my partner, \NI don't think anyone'll give you a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.08,Flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,But is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.46,Flashback,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.71,Flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.82,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've always been a bit scared
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:24.27,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,to get too close with anyone in game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.90,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say I was on my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:30.85,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,But then I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.11,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:37.33,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like you really enjoyed\N playing this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:40.99,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It made me enjoy the game more myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:45.74,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Hayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:46.99,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.00,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:54.50,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,What? Lily-san, what are \Nyou trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.73,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,...become my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:06.76,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Partner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.27,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:13.59,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,My main is a support class, so I end up \Ngrouping with a lot of different people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:16.77,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,but I've really enjoyed \Ngrouping up with you lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.65,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,You... have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:21.56,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I have all sorts of reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.16,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,but just to put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:28.91,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I feel most at peace when \Nplaying together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.67,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:35.02,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,My heart won't stop racing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.44,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.17,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,So much so that the word "overjoyed" \Ndoesn't even do it justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.17,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since \NI've felt this excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.71,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call having a crush, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.30,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.81,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be thinking \Nlike this in my thirties?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:53.58,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,She's even a girl! I'm sure there's \Nnothing romantic going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.69,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,And first and foremost, \Nshe's someone I only know online!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.52,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.77,Main_Italics,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.99,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:06.70,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:10.70,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.71,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.71,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.48,Main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Hayashi-san, um... Does this mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:24.30,Main,Hayashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm looking forward to being \Nyour partner from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:30.94,Main,Pokotarou,0000,0000,0000,,So she really did have an ulterior motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.78,Main,Lilac,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how stupidly happy those two \NMMO junkies are! Damn, I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:37.86,Main,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you found someone you \Nget along so well with, Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.95,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Lily-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.96,sign_31420_350_Lily__Hayashi_sa,# log,0000,0000,0000,,Lily:  Hayashi-san, um... Does this mean...? \NHayashi:  Yes. I'm looking forward to being your partner \NHayashi:  from now on! \NLily:  I feel the same way, Hayashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:40.10,Next Episode,# text,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:27.59,Main,Kanbe,0000,0000,0000,,Once you know, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.52,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.37,Main,Koiwai,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd go out on a date with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:31.47,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.97,Main,Lilac,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you want something, \Nit slips out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:39.51,Main,Moriko,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4, "Like a Maiden in Love."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:40.18,Next EP Title,# text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,1)}Episode 4 \N{\fs20}Like a Maiden in Love